    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required credibility level. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against required level 3 due to single ASTM F1717 test condition; this shortfall is accepted as consistent with regulatory precedent for pedicle screw submissions and is offset by the strong quantitative validation evidence across all three QoIs (E/uval < 1.96, relative difference < 10%). The FEA modeling framework is assessed as credible for the stated COU at Medium model risk.",
    "decidedAt": "2026-04-19T00:00:00Z"
